title: Start
---

Rain taps softly against the window.
A cramped studio apartment. Bills scattered across a small table. The room is dim except for the light of a phone screen.
The Player stares at the screen. 
<<play_animation Player Black>>

Player: …Rent… electricity… overdue notice?

The Player exhales.

Player: I can’t keep stretching it like this.

Her stomach growls. 

Player: …I really need a job. Anything at this point.

She goes to job search site and scrolls through job listings.

Part-time Café Staff – Experience required
Convenience Store Night Shift – Minimum wage
Warehouse Sorting – Heavy lifting required

Player: Minimum wage… heavy lifting… I won’t survive on that.

She scrolls further down.
The scrolling slows.

Private Residence | High Pay – Paid Immediately After Completion, No Experience Required

Player: ... One week?

She taps the listing.

- Clean designated areas only
- Do not enter restricted rooms
- Follow all instructions strictly
- Live-out position
- Generous compensation
A phone number is listed below. No company name. No address.

Player: ... Private residence?

She frowns.

Player: No company name… no photos… no reviews…

She scrolls. Nothing more.

Player: That's suspicious. But...

She breathes in.

Player: The pay. 

She rereads the number.

Player: That’s more than I’d make in a month.

The rain outside grows slightly louder.

What should I do?

-> Ignore it.
    Player: It’s probably some scam.
    Player: ... Or even worse. 
    A small pause.
    Player: ... But what if it isn't?
    She glances back at the unpaid bills.
    Player: I just need one week.
    <<jump PhoneCall>>
-> Call now.
    <<jump PhoneCall>>

===
title: PhoneCall
---
<<play_animation Player Grey>>

The phone rings once. 
Twice.

Click.

Land Lady: Hello?

Her voice is steady. Almost too steady.

Player: Ah, he- hello. I'm calling you about the cleaning job...

A brief pause.

Land Lady: A-ha. You saw the listing. 

Player: Yes... 

(Story ongoing)

Let's move down to go to the workplace. 

<<change_clothes Player Maid>>


===
